# Cursor Orchestrator — File Ownership

## Rule

Do not create a file that is not listed below for the phase you are in, unless you first add it to docs/PROGRESS.md and get it agreed. Do not modify files owned by a previous phase unless there is an explicit note in docs/PROGRESS.md authorizing the change.

## Phase 0 — Rules & Documentation

Creates:

- `.cursor/rules/00-project-scope.mdc`
- `.cursor/rules/01-architecture.mdc`
- `.cursor/rules/02-file-ownership.mdc`
- `.cursor/rules/03-handoff-protocol.mdc`
- `.cursor/rules/04-progress-tracking.mdc`
- `.cursor/rules/05-coding-standards.mdc`
- `.cursor/rules/06-no-hallucination.mdc`
- `docs/SCOPE.md`
- `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`
- `docs/PROGRESS.md`
- `docs/SCHEMAS.md`
- `docs/agent-handoffs/TEMPLATE.md`

