Modifies (authorized):

- `docs/PROGRESS.md` — Phase 1 and Phase 2 sections updated to COMPLETE; checkboxes filled.

## Locked After Creation

Once a file is created and marked complete in PROGRESS.md, do not refactor or rename it without documenting the change in PROGRESS.md and in the next handoff document. This keeps handoffs accurate.
